{1: '1', 2: 'Lee', 3: "Commandant, I have found a suitable school for Nanami with Celica's help. What say we send her over?", 4: '1'}
{2: 'You certainly work fast.', 3: '5', 4: 'Oh... Okay...', 5: '6'}
{2: 'Lee', 3: "It's not like we have other jobs on our hands at the moment.", 4: '1'}
{2: 'Lee', 3: "It's just going to school, nothing special.", 4: '1'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Nanami', 3: "Hm, Nanami doesn't want to leave Commandant.", 4: '2'}
{2: 'Nanami', 3: "You see, when the Earth is reclaimed, everyone will be free! It won't be too late for my research!", 4: '2'}
{2: 'Lee', 3: "The war's not looking good for us though. And before that time comes, can you promise that you'll never cause trouble again like last time out of selfishness?", 4: '1'}
{2: 'Nanami', 3: "Nanami's not selfish... It's just the time limit of the mission...", 4: '2'}
{2: 'Lee', 3: 'Time limit?', 4: '1'}
{2: 'Lee', 3: "I don't know when that limit is, but isn't that all the more reason for you to finish your research as soon as possible?", 4: '1'}
{2: 'Nanami', 3: "But... but Nanami doesn't want to leave Commandant!", 4: '2'}
{2: "I don't want Nanami to leave either!", 3: '17', 4: "Lee, don't let Nanami leave!", 5: '17'}
{2: 'Lee', 3: 'You two... Why do I feel like the villain...', 4: '1'}
{2: 'Lee', 3: "Truth be told, I'm not interested in Nanami's mission at all, I just want her to stop making a mess of the base.", 4: '1'}
{2: 'Lee', 3: 'Can you promise to not destroy anything out of boredom from now on?', 4: '1'}
{2: 'Eh?', 3: '23', 4: 'I think you should say "yes" here.', 5: '23'}
{2: 'Nanami', 3: 'But Nanami will try her best starting from today.', 4: '2'}
{2: 'Nanami', 3: "Whether it's battles, daily tasks, or other missions, Nanami will take care of them all before the time limit!", 4: '2'}
{2: 'Nanami', 3: "In return, please become Nanami's finest research subject, Commandant.", 4: '2'}
{2: 'Nanami', 3: 'Humans live in groups, and there are bound to be excellent individuals in a group.', 4: '2'}
{2: 'Nanami', 3: "And that individual is the most important research subject! At least that's what Nanami thinks.", 4: '2'}
{2: 'What are you talking about?', 3: '28', 4: 'Are you talking about me?', 5: '29'}
{2: 'Nanami', 3: 'What Nanami means to say is, please become the most outstanding human, Commandant!', 4: '2'}
{2: 'Nanami', 3: "Hehe! That's right!", 4: '2'}
{2: 'Nanami', 3: "Because you're the only one qualified to be my research subject and my commandant!", 4: '2'}
{2: 'Nanami', 3: "And the book did say that... Only an outing between two individuals who like each other can be called... a date. ANYONE—ELSE—WON'T—DO.", 4: '2'}
